name: Legal consequences of generated content with Damien Riehl, VP of Litigation Workflow & Analytics Content at vLex (Practical AI #232)
summary: As a technologist, coder, and lawyer, few people are better equipped to discuss the legal and practical consequences of generative AI than Damien Riehl. He demonstrated this a couple years ago by generating, writing to disk, and then releasing every possible musical melody. Damien joins us to answer our many questions ...
